\" href=\"/book/53258.html\">\n                <img src=\"https://img-tailor.11222.cn/bcv/big/11590353258_sa.jpg\">\n            </a>\n            <div class=\"bookTitle\">\n                <a class=\"bname\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"/book/53258.html\">斗破苍穹</a>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"bauthor\">作者：天蚕土豆</div>\n            <div class=\"tag\">\n                \n                <span class=\"tag\">传统玄幻</span>\n                \n                <span class=\"tag\">修士</span>\n                \n                <span class=\"tag\">修炼</span>\n                \n                <span class=\"tag\">升级</span>\n                \n                <span class=\"tag\">少年</span>\n                \n            </div>\n            <ul class=\"lastchapter clear\">\n                <li>异界大陆</li>\n                <li>522.4万字</li>\n                <li>完结</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>2025-06-25 09:49更新</li>\n            </ul>\n            \n            <p class=\"bookDesc\">这里是属于斗气的世界，没有花俏艳丽的魔法，有的，仅仅是繁衍到巅峰的斗气！新书等级制度：斗者，斗师，大斗师，斗灵，斗王，斗皇，斗宗，斗尊，斗圣，斗帝。……</p>\n            \n            <div class=\"operates clear\">\n                <div class=\"left\">\n                    <span class=\"btn read\">\n                        <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"/reader?bid=53258\">立即阅读</a>\n                    </span>\n                    <span class=\"btn js-addShelf\" data-bid=\"53258\" data-clog=\"shelf-shelf$$bid=53258\">+书架</span>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    \n    <div class=\"searchlist-main\" data-clog=\"search-books\">\n        \n        <ul class=\"clearfix page-width\">\n            \n            <li>\n                <a class=\"book-cover\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"/book/9163025.html\" data-clog=\"1$$bid=9163025&amp;pagearea=1\">\n                    <img src=\"https://img-tailor.11222.cn/bcv/big/202508121049599341_sa.jpg\">\n                </a>\n                <a class=\"ellipsis\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"/book/9163025.html\" data-clog=\"1$$bid=9163025&amp;pagearea=1\">\n                    叶凡穿越<i class=\"hl\">斗</i><i class=\"hl\">破</i><i class=\"hl\">苍</i><i class=\"hl\">穹</i>\n                </a>\n                <p class=\"book-autor\">\n                    <a href=\"/author/一只小春秋?aid=4953930\">作者：一只小春秋</a>\n                </p>\n                <div class=\"category\">小说同人</div>\n                <p class=\"book-newc\">谁在称无敌，哪个敢言不败！北斗星域至尊大战落幕，黑暗动乱终结。融合大成圣体躯壳逆战至尊的叶凡失去意识，魂魄飘到了斗气大陆，一个曾经的天才，如今的废柴萧炎身上。【不压战力】【无敌流】【弱女主】（ps.不会乱搞cp，配角人设贴合原著）</p>\n            </li>\n            \n            <li>\n                <a class=\"book-cover\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"/book/8855023.html\" data-clog=\"2$$bid=8855023&amp;pagearea=1\">\n                    <img src=\"https://img-tailor.11222.cn/bcv/big/202308110934533126_sa.jpg\">\n                </a>\n                <a class=\"ellipsis\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"/book/8855023.html\" data-clog=\"2$$bid=8855023&amp;pagearea=1\">\n                    <i class=\"hl\">斗</i><i class=\"hl\">破</i><i class=\"hl\">苍</i><i class=\"hl\">穹</i>之至高真神\n                </a>\n                <p class=\"book-autor\">\n                    <a href=\"/author/落日精灵?aid=4740489\">作者：落日精灵</a>\n                </p>\n                <div class=\"category\">小说同人</div>\n                <p class=\"book-newc\">大千世界，位面集结，万道争锋，真龙降世，一位突破位面桎梏的炎帝萧炎，降临在这片浩瀚的无尽世界，会演绎怎样的传奇？各方天之至尊层出不穷，追逐那令人向往的主宰之路，探索主宰之上的神之领域。等级制度：至尊境、地至尊、天至尊、主宰境、神祇境</p>\n            </li>\n            \n            <li>\n                <a class=\"book-cover\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"/book/9014647.html\" data-clog=\"3$$bid=9014647&amp;pagearea=1\">\n                    <img src=\"https://img-tailor.11222.cn/bcv/big/202503121718024383_sa.jpg\">\n                </a>\n                <a class=\"ellipsis\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"/book/9014647.html\" data-clog=\"3$$bid=9014647&amp;pagearea=1\">\n                    <i class=\"hl\">斗</i><i class=\"hl\">破</i><i class=\"hl\">苍</i><i class=\"hl\">穹</i>之魔帝萧炎\n                </a>\n                <p class=\"book-autor\">\n                    <a href=\"/author/朽木罢了?aid=4828744\">作者：朽木罢了</a>\n                </p>\n                <div class=\"category\">小说同人</div>\n                <p class=\"book-newc\">众叛亲离，孤独一人成为盖世强者的魔怒圣者萧炎，在探寻斗帝之秘时，却穿过了时间之门。原本处于黑化线的他却重生到了正常线的斗气大陆，经历注定不平凡的人生……</p>\n            </li>\n            \n            <li>\n                <a class=\"book-cover\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"/book/9155156.html\" data-clog=\"4$$bid=9155156&amp;pagearea=1\">\n                    <img src=\"https://img-tailor.11222.cn/bcv/big/202507272346095613_sa.jpg\">\n                </a>\n                <a class=\"ellipsis\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"/book/9155156.html\" data-clog=\"4$$bid=9155156&amp;pagearea=1\">\n                    <i class=\"hl\">斗</i><i class=\"hl\">破</i>：权御<i class=\"hl\">苍</i><i class=\"hl\">穹</i>\n                </a>\n                <p class=\"book-autor\">\n                    <a href=\"/author/李向阳?aid=1360850\">作者：李向阳</a>\n                </p>\n                <div class=\"category\">小说同人</div>\n                <p class=\"book-newc\">我本身一名普普通通的上班族，刚加完班的我在回家的路上却出了车祸。再一次睁眼，周围却是别样的环境。正在我疑惑时，一段不属于我的记忆涌入其中。我才明白我魂穿到了斗破苍穹中，而且还是古族第二强者古列唯一的儿子。</p>\n            </li>\n            \n            <li>\n                <a class=\"book-cover\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"/book/9018743.html\" data-clog=\"5$$bid=9018743&amp;pagearea=1\">\n                    <img src=\"https://img-tailor.11222.cn/bcv/big/202408301755056389_sa.jpg\">\n                </a>\n                <a class=\"ellipsis\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"/book/9018743.html\" data-clog=\"5$$bid=9018743&amp;pagearea=1\">\n                    <i class=\"hl\">斗</i>火之大<i class=\"hl\">破</i><i class=\"hl\">苍</i><i class=\"hl\">穹</i>\n                </a>\n                <p class=\"book-autor\">\n                    <a href=\"/author/金子金子?aid=4831146\">作者：金子金子</a>\n                </p>\n                <div class=\"category\">异界大陆</div>\n                <p class=\"book-newc\">在斗火大陆，有句格言：男人没有火，活得像娘们；女人没有火，活得像花瓶！在斗火大陆，不怕你火大，就怕你没有火！没有火，在别人眼里，你就是个废物！美丽的少女香雪儿却喜欢废物少年金斗焕，趁着爹娘不在家，把金斗焕带回家，生米煮成熟饭。老爹城主大人回到家，宠爱之下只好马上安排给她办喜事。谁知反对她嫁给废物的人排满整条街，喜宴上还闹出了人命······</p>\n            </li>\n            \n            <li>\n                <a class=\"book-cover\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"/book/6240671.html\" data-clog=\"6$$bid=6240671&amp;pagearea=1\">\n                    <img src=\"https://img-tailor.11222.cn/bcv/big/202208020956472396_sa.jpg\">\n                </a>\n                <a class=\"ellipsis\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"/book/6240671.html\" data-clog=\"6$$bid=6240671&amp;pagearea=1\">\n                    灵<i class=\"hl\">破</i><i class=\"hl\">苍</i><i class=\"hl\">穹</i>\n                </a>\n                <p class=\"book-autor\">\n                    <a href=\"/author/心跳的瞬间?aid=718313\">作者：心跳的瞬间</a>\n                </p>\n                <div class=\"category\">东方玄幻</div>\n                <p class=\"book-newc\">一个从青叶小镇走出来的少年，偶然机会解除体内封印，从此文能一念惊天地，武能一掌碎山河。灵武兼修，踏遍诸天万界，踩踏无数天才，引红颜知己竞折腰！</p>\n            </li>\n            \n            <li>\n                <a class=\"book-cover\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"/book/155346.html\" data-clog=\"7$$bid=155346&amp;pagearea=1\">\n                    <img src=\"https://img-tailor.11222.cn/bcv/big/202207201724532755_sa.jpg\">\n                </a>\n                <a class=\"ellipsis\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"/book/155346.html\" data-clog=\"7$$bid=155346&amp;pagearea=1\">\n                    龙<i class=\"hl\">破</i><i class=\"hl\">苍</i><i class=\"hl\">穹</i>\n                </a>\n                <p class=\"book-autor\">\n                    <a href=\"/author/血友人生?aid=95804\">作者：血友人生</a>\n                </p>\n                <div class=\"category\">东方玄幻</div>\n                <p class=\"book-newc\">华夏乃龙之传人，这只是一个传说，但龙飞天却真的证实了这个传说。一个荒唐的误会，让龙飞天变成了龙家的废物少爷，为了让母亲不被欺负，为了变得强大，龙飞天不畏强势，见神杀神，遇鬼灭鬼，一步步向着颠峰迈进。</p>\n            </li>\n            \n            <li>\n                <a class=\"book-cover\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"/book/2553661.html\" data-clog=\"8$$bid=2553661&amp;pagearea=1\">\n                    <img src=\"https://img-tailor.11222.cn/bcv/big/201606061124099595_sa.jpg\">\n                </a>\n                <a class=\"ellipsis\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"/book/2553661.html\" data-clog=\"8$$bid=2553661&amp;pagearea=1\">\n                    雷<i class=\"hl\">破</i><i class=\"hl\">苍</i><i class=\"hl\">穹</i>\n                </a>\n                <p class=\"book-autor\">\n                    <a href=\"/author/明朝有酒?aid=1377907\">作者：明朝有酒</a>\n                </p>\n                <div class=\"category\">东方玄幻</div>\n                <p class=\"book-newc\">传承逆天神力、练成天外化身、手控辟邪神雷、驯服超级魔兽，一路披荆斩棘，最终踏上终极强者巅峰！雷霆大陆风起云涌，少年雷羽破九幽，战雷霆，独领天下，逆天而行，走出自己的雷道，成就无上雷帝！</p>\n            </li>\n            \n            <li>\n                <a class=\"book-cover\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"/book/156444.html\" data-clog=\"9$$bid=156444&amp;pagearea=1\">\n                    <img src=\"https://img-tailor.11222.cn/bcv/big/202403151624031063_sa.jpg\">\n                </a>\n                <a class=\"ellipsis\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"/book/156444.html\" data-clog=\"9$$bid=156444&amp;pagearea=1\">\n                    剑<i class=\"hl\">破</i><i class=\"hl\">苍</i><i class=\"hl\">穹</i>\n                </a>\n                <p class=\"book-autor\">\n                    <a href=\"/author/猪爬树?aid=171747\">作者：猪爬树</a>\n                </p>\n                <div class=\"category\">异界大陆</div>\n                <p class=\"book-newc\">姜嗣本是蜀山剑派的天才，却穿越到轩辕大陆的废物身上。冲破封印，越阶制敌，从此蜀山道法被誉为神技！休妻，斗狠，杀伐，尽显强者风范！剑指宗门，大扬姜家之威！火炼灵丹，赚尽世间钱财！今生知己，让他摆脱前世丧妻之痛。暗杀偷袭，能否阻拦他踏上巅峰的脚步？杀尽天下人，只为一览佳人，笑傲苍穹……</p>\n            </li>\n            \n        </ul>\n        <div class=\"store-paging\">\n            <div class=\"comp-web-pages\"><span class=\"cp-wp-page active\">首页</span><span class=\"cp-wp-page display\">上一页</span><span class=\"cp-wp-page active\">1</span><span class=\"cp-wp-page\"><a href=\"/search?keyword=%E6%96%97%E7%A0%B4%E8%8B%8D%E7%A9%B9&amp;page=2\" target=\"_self\">2</a></span><span class=\"cp-wp-page\"><a href=\"/search?keyword=%E6%96%97%E7%A0%B4%E8%8B%8D%E7%A9%B9&amp;page=3\" target=\"_self\">3</a></span><span class=\"cp-wp-ellipsis display\">...</span><span class=\"cp-wp-page\"><a href=\"/search?keyword=%E6%96%97%E7%A0%B4%E8%8B%8D%E7%A9%B9&amp;page=11\" target=\"_self\">11</a></span><span class=\"cp-wp-page\"><a href=\"/search?keyword=%E6%96%97%E7%A0%B4%E8%8B%8D%E7%A9%B9&amp;page=2\" target=\"_self\">下一页</a></span><span class=\"cp-wp-page\"><a href=\"/search?keyword=%E6%96%97%E7%A0%B4%E8%8B%8D%E7%A9%B9&amp;page=11\" target=\"_self\">尾页</a></span></div>\n        </div>\n        \n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\t<div class=\"comp-web-bottom\">\n\t\t<div class=\"page-width\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"cp-wb-copyright clear cp-wb-links cp-wb-links-internal\">\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"/about/lxwm\" rel=\"nofollow\">联系我们</a>\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"/about/gywm\" rel=\"nofollow\">关于书旗</a>\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"/about/tgsm\" rel=\"nofollow\">投稿声明</a>\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://render-web.shuqireader.com/render/sq-base/page/self_examine_doc/?serviceWorkerOn=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">自审制度</a>\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"/about/bqsm\" rel=\"nofollow\">版权声明</a>\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"/about/cjwt\" rel=\"nofollow\">常见问题</a>\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://terms.alicdn.com/legal-agreement/terms/privacy_policy_full/20231020143115179/20231020143115179.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">隐私协议</a>\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://terms.alicdn.com/legal-agreement/terms/suit_bu1_other/suit_bu1_other202009181421_79060.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">用户协议</a>\n\t\t\t\t<!--% <a href=\"http://weibo.com/aliwenxue\" target=\"_blank\">网站微博</a> %-->\n\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"cp-wb-copyright clear  cp-wb-links-outernal\">\n\t\t\t\t友情链接：\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.alibabagroup.com/cn/global/home\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"left\">阿里巴巴集团</a>\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.taobao.com\" target=\"_blank\">淘宝网</a>\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.tmall.co